<br>
Subati stares at the parchment before, his demeanor unreadable, his eyes unblinking.<br>
<br>
Two phrases over and over again, mumble from his lips.<br>
<br>
&quot;I bet she dies in two minutes,&quot; <br>
<br>
&quot;No, no...she's tough...I bet she can last 5 minutes,&quot; <br>
<br>
The rage overcomes, the Fathers Hatred courses, ney tears through, bringing the berserker upon him. For a moment, he becomes the beast that is his name sake.<br>
<br>
With one slam of mailed fist, the table beneath shatters as chrystal.<br>
<br>
Howling, burning with anger, he screams into the night &quot;I bet they both die in one minute, should I find them.&quot;<br>
<br>
The thought, somehow calms him,<br>
<br>
&quot;Yes... maybe one day, Selilya would enjoy them placed in the arena, and made to duel.&quot; Smiling at the thought, &quot;Then we could wager on how long each of them would last.&quot;<br>
<br>
Smiling at the thought, he places the heavy silk clothe over his mounted lightstone, and heads for bed.<br>
<br>
&quot;Another item for my growing list.&quot; He thinks for a brief moment, before making ready to sleep. <br>
